          <span class="compare-eyebrow">Comparison · Last verified {lastVerified}</span>
          <h1>Kintone vs Salesforce for Japan SMEs</h1>
          <p class="compare-lead">
            Both platforms are sold as the answer for Japan businesses that need
            better systems. Neither is universally right. Here's the honest
            breakdown. Pricing, fit, implementation reality, and when each one
            actually makes sense.
          </p>
          <div class="compare-meta">
            <span>By <a href="/about/" rel="author">Matt Ketchum</a></span>
            <span>·</span>
            <span>Tokyo</span>
            <span>·</span>
            <span>~10 min read</span>
          </div>
        </header>

